"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The feature of the Wolf of Wall Street is that they know how to carry each other's sedan chair, combine to harvest opponents, and try to avoid involution. This is also an important difference between the regular army and the bandits and gangsters who flank each other every day, and is an important reason why the former is far more powerful than the latter.\\n\\nIf we recognize that Wall Street financial institutions are a powerful force, then it may be capable of delaying the arrival of a bear market, but it is absolutely incapable of preventing the arrival of a bear market.\\n\\nBecause in this market, it will encounter a terrible opponent that it has never encountered before-the giant whale.\\n\\nThe gods fight, the little ghost suffers. What we small retail investors need to do is to be good at using the \\\"free rider\\\" strategy in game theory. Concentrate on making a Bazi Jue and watch these big guys perform hard and quietly. Eat melon and watch the show, make a profit by the way.\",\"timestamp\":1634475076,\"title\":\"The feature of this cycle is different from the past, that is, the regular army's approach. However, Wall Street is a mercenary, not a government army. Formally trained armed forces are enough to deal with grass bandits.\"},\"digest\":\"g0gsdcGw02gG8IydVjKYO7fVvyUp5Z2DjXeIl9McNlo\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x22f051a8d3a4e048877D965f683Fdac7db09D92f\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"oelE6UrZY_iGn640lDKassfp2OmGBcKC-q0A1Bby6Ys\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"h_3UkVD0dWRNtG2-3h4UuxPh4tERVZaf8F-2Ep2qnD8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"-woe6Jh2KIkC13NfSSVS6-Skp62LS0P-Rj9lnfl4iRKzQ9wyCd9la8AOsVe3xOUPhPRxFWuslUOx77pRY1OJug\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x9a5b7ce4df00e6112a575eeca01130fe334738908f6ae6ab42615319611838d8597bb9c84ab49cd6e744462a2482719e7f2d611615c4e4ff0fe4956b3380c82c1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz